### AgentTreasury API — Manual Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:3001

@base = http://localhost:3001
@testAddress = 0xf39Fd6e51aad88F6F4ce6aB8827279cffFb92266

### ==================== Health ====================

### Health check
GET {{base}}/health

### ==================== Dashboard ====================

### Get dashboard data
GET {{base}}/api/dashboard

### ==================== Treasury ====================

### Get treasury state
GET {{base}}/api/treasury

### Sync treasury state
POST {{base}}/api/treasury/sync

### Emergency pause
POST {{base}}/api/emergency/pause

### ==================== Credit ====================

### Get credit profile (must evaluate first)
GET {{base}}/api/credit/{{testAddress}}

### Evaluate credit (creates/updates profile)
POST {{base}}/api/credit/{{testAddress}}/evaluate

### Get user loans
GET {{base}}/api/credit/{{testAddress}}/loans

### Get all active loans
GET {{base}}/api/loans

### ==================== Borrow & Repay ====================

### Borrow 100 USDt (amount in wei, 6 decimals)
POST {{base}}/api/credit/{{testAddress}}/borrow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": "100000000"
}

### Repay loan #0 — 50 USDt
POST {{base}}/api/credit/{{testAddress}}/repay
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loanId": 0,
  "amount": "50000000"
}

### ==================== Yield ====================

### Get yield opportunities
GET {{base}}/api/yield/opportunities

### Invest in yield
POST {{base}}/api/yield/invest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "protocol": "aave",
  "amount": "1000000000",
  "apy": 4.5
}

### ==================== Withdrawal ====================

### Propose withdrawal
POST {{base}}/api/treasury/withdrawal/propose
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "{{testAddress}}",
  "amount": "500000000"
}

### ==================== Decisions ====================

### Get all recent decisions
GET {{base}}/api/decisions

### Get treasury decisions only
GET {{base}}/api/decisions?type=treasury

### Get credit decisions only
GET {{base}}/api/decisions?type=credit
